--// Aurora UI Library
--// A minimalistic, beautiful UI library for Roblox
--// Version: 7.0.0
--
--  Improvements over v6:
--    [PERF]  Slider / ColorPicker drag connections are created on drag-start and
--            destroyed on drag-end instead of living for the entire session.
--    [FIX]   AddShadow ZIndex is now guarded: math.max(1, parent.ZIndex - 1).
--    [FIX]   Slider SetValue now fires OnChanged and cfg.Callback.
--    [FIX]   HexInput resets to current color on blur (not only on Enter).
--    [FIX]   SetEnabled(false) called twice no longer re-dims already-dim text.
--    [FIX]   Minimize restores to live size, not the original config size.
--    [FIX]   Keybind cancel connection is scoped so it can't fire during listen start.
--    [FIX]   Dropdown / SearchDropdown / MultiSelect / ColorPicker now go through
--            BaseFrame-equivalent sizing so LayoutOrder is always correct.
--    [API]   Dropdown & MultiSelect both expose SetOptions(newOptions).
--    [API]   Window:SelectTab() accepts a Tab object OR a numeric index.
--    [API]   ColorPicker supports an optional alpha channel (cfg.Alpha = true).
--    [UX]    Magic layout numbers replaced with named constants.
--    [UX]    CreateColorPicker split into clearly-labelled sub-sections.

